pesticide.PPE: Long-sleeved shirt and long pants; Chemical-resistant gloves made of barrier laminate, butyl rubber ≥14 mils, nitrile rubber ≥14 mils, neoprene rubber ≥14 mils, polyvinyl chloride ≥14 mils, or Viton ≥14 mils; Shoes plus socks

Safety_Information.general_Info: CAUTION. Harmful if absorbed through skin. Avoid contact with skin or clothing.
Safety_Information.if_On_Skin: Take off contaminated clothing; Rinse skin immediately with plenty of water for 15-20 minutes; Call a poison control center or doctor for treatment advice.
